spec_data.Name: python2-openstack-nose-plugin
spec_data.Description:
openstack.nose_plugin provides a nose plugin that allow's nosetests output to
mimic the output of openstack's run_tests.py.
This package provides Python 2 build of openstack.nose_plugin.

spec_data.Summary: openstack run_tests.py style output for nosetests
